headline.main: AMERICAN ACCEPTANCE OF PRESENT FOR BRITAIN

lead_paragraph: Vegetable seeds for the use of the Queen of England and residents of her estate at Sandringham were prepared for shipment yesterday with the endorsement of Mrs. Franklin D. Roosevelt as a sponsor for the organization known as American Seeds for British Soil.
